指令: ./program [資料數量 M] [傳送速率 R] [consumer數量 N] [buffer size B]
印出格式:
    This is message 1
    This is message 2
    This is message 3
                   .
                   .
                   .
    This is message N

    Total messages: X
    Sum of received messages by all consumers: Y
    Loss rate: Z